org.linqs.psl.reasoner.term.online

Class OnlineTermStore<T extends ReasonerTerm>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.linqs.psl.reasoner.term.streaming.StreamingTermStore<T>
      • org.linqs.psl.reasoner.term.online.OnlineTermStore<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<T>, TermStore<T,GroundAtom>, VariableTermStore<T,GroundAtom>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SGDOnlineTermStore

    public abstract class OnlineTermStore<T extends ReasonerTerm>
extends StreamingTermStore<T>
    A term store that supports online operations. The numPages class variable represents the number of active pages in OnlineTermStores.
